  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb4\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1 64 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "64 people were arrested for selling chicken eggs",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Consumer Affairs Authority, a case has been filed against 64 traders who sold eggs at a higher price than the fixed price without taking them into account.",
        "The special gazette fixing the maximum retail price for eggs was published on 19th midnight and was implemented from that night.",
        "Accordingly, the maximum retail price of a white egg has been fixed at 43 rupees and the maximum retail price of a red or brown egg has been fixed at 45 rupees.",
        "However, the Consumer Affairs Council has announced that legal action has been taken against traders who sold eggs above the fixed price."
      ],
